      <title>据 Sky 报道，泰晤士水务公司因股息面临 4000 万英镑罚款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/thames-water-faces-40-million-fine-over-dividends-sky-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据天空电视台援引英国水务公司一位消息人士的话报道，英国水务供应商泰晤士水务公司因违反股息支付规定而面临超过 4000 万英镑（5100 万美元）的罚款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/thames-water-faces-40-million-fine-over-dividends-sky-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 10:28:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊斯坦布尔市零售通胀率创 2022 年 12 月以来最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/istanbul-city-retail-inflation-hits-highest-since-december-2022</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊斯坦布尔年度零售通胀率加速至2022年12月以来的最高水平，因为土耳其的价格涨幅在5月份达到峰值后预计将在下半年下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/istanbul-city-retail-inflation-hits-highest-since-december-2022</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 09:57:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港称 11 家加密货币交易所即将获得许可</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/hong-kong-says-11-crypto-exchanges-are-closer-to-getting-permits</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港证券监管机构表示，在推出数字资产规则手册以试图打造该行业中心一年后，11 家加密货币交易所距离获得许可证又近了一步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/hong-kong-says-11-crypto-exchanges-are-closer-to-getting-permits</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 09:00:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国支付监管机构负责人因退款问题辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/head-of-uk-payments-regulator-steps-down-amid-refunds-backlash</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着人们对新的欺诈退款规则的反对声越来越大，英国支付行业监管机构的董事总经理即将辞职。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/head-of-uk-payments-regulator-steps-down-amid-refunds-backlash</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 08:50:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股票交易者如何应对欧洲议会选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/a-stock-trader-s-guide-to-navigating-the-eu-parliament-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[预计下周欧洲议会选举将对民粹主义政党带来提振，这可能会动摇欧盟的气候目标和政策重点，可再生能源、汽车制造商和工业公司的股价可能会受到影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/a-stock-trader-s-guide-to-navigating-the-eu-parliament-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 07:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>标普下调法国信用评级 马克龙处境更艰难</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/macron-gets-debt-reprimand-as-s-p-hits-france-with-downgrade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[标准普尔全球评级下调了法国的评级，玷污了总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙的债务管理记录，并使他在欧洲选举前一周陷入了更深的政治困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/macron-gets-debt-reprimand-as-s-p-hits-france-with-downgrade</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 20:23:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
